definition:
actions:
- deploy:
    failure_retry: 2
    images:
      kernel: {image_arg: '-kernel {kernel} -append "console=ttyS0,115200 root=/dev/hda
          debug verbose"', url: 'https://download.automotivelinux.org/AGL/release/dab/4.0.2/qemux86-64/deploy/images/qemux86-64/bzImage'}
      ramdisk: {compression: xz, image_arg: '-drive format=raw,file={ramdisk}', url: 'https://download.automotivelinux.org/AGL/release/dab/4.0.2/qemux86-64/deploy/images/qemux86-64/agl-demo-platform-qemux86-64.ext4.xz'}
    os: oe
    timeout: {minutes: 15}
    to: tmpfs
- boot:
    auto_login: {login_prompt: 'login:', username: root}
    media: tmpfs
    method: qemu
    prompts: ['root@qemux86-64:~', '/ #']
    timeout: {minutes: 10}
    transfer_overlay: {download_command: wget, unpack_command: tar -C / -xvpf}
- test:
    definitions:
    - {from: git, name: busybox, path: test-suites/short-smoke/busybox.yaml, repository: 'https://git.automotivelinux.org/src/qa-testdefinitions'}
    - {from: git, name: smoke-tests-basic, path: test-suites/short-smoke/smoke-tests-basic.yaml,
      repository: 'https://git.automotivelinux.org/src/qa-testdefinitions'}
    - {from: git, name: service-check, path: test-suites/short-smoke/service-check.yaml,
      repository: 'https://git.automotivelinux.org/src/qa-testdefinitions'}
- test:
    definitions:
    - from: inline
      name: health-test
      path: inline/health-test.yaml
      repository:
        metadata:
          description: Inline test to validate test framewrok health
          format: Lava-Test Test Definition 1.0
          name: inline-test
          os: [debian]
          scope: [functional]
        run:
          steps: [lava-test-set start set-pass, lava-test-case always-pass --shell
              true, lava-test-set stop set-pass, lava-test-set start set-fail, lava-test-case
              always-fail --shell false, lava-test-set stop set-fail]
    timeout: {minutes: 2}
- test:
    definitions:
    - {from: git, name: yocto-ptest, path: test-suites/yocto-ptest.yaml, repository: 'https://git.automotivelinux.org/src/qa-testdefinitions'}
context:
  arch: x86_64
  extra_options: ['-cpu qemu64,+ssse3,+sse4.1,+sse4.2,+popcnt -m 1048 -soundhw hda']
  no_kvm: false
device_type: qemu
job_name: AGL-short-smoke-wip
metadata: {git.branch: agl-branch, image.type: AGL, job.arch: x86_64, job.name: AGL-short-smoke-wip,
  job.original: !!python/unicode 'http://example.com/scheduler/job/2127', kernel.defconfig: defconfig+CONFIG_AGL=y,
  kernel.defconfig_base: defconfig, kernel.tree: AGL-kernel-tree, kernel.version: AGL-kernel-version,
  platform.mach: x86, platform.name: qemu, vcs.url: 'https://download.automotivelinux.org/AGL/release/dab/4.0.2/qemux86-64/deploy/images/qemux86-64/'}
notify:
  callback: {content-type: json, dataset: all, method: POST, token: 52e284ae-8101-4e0a-91ac-44cec9afdb40,
    url: 'http://api.dev.baylibre.com/callback/lava/test?lab_name=lab-baylibre-legacy&status={STATUS}&status_string={STATUS_STRING}'}
  criteria: {status: finished}
priority: medium
timeouts:
  action: {minutes: 15}
  connection: {minutes: 5}
  job: {minutes: 30}
visibility: public
